      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "sq.gr.sepal(adata) Our re-implementation in Numba achieves greater computational efficiency (Supplementary Fig. 1). Centrality scores... The time t the gene takes to reach consensus is then used a 'Sepal score' and indicates the degree of spatial variability of the gene.",
