    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/categorical-annotation-handling-in-omics-data/010",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "sq.gr.nhood_enrichment(adata, cluster_key=\"<cluster_key>\")... The association between label pairs in the connectivity graph is estimated by counting the sum of nodes that belong to classes i and j (for example cluster annotation)",
      "asbval:note": "Paper explicitly uses cluster_key parameter to reference categorical annotations.",
