    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/categorical-annotation-handling-in-omics-data/011",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Clusters of enriched cell types (such as 'Lateral plate mesoderm' with 'Allantois' and 'Intermediate mesoderm' clusters, 'Endothelium' with 'Hematoendothelial progenitors'; Fig. 2b) are consistent with the original publication and the spatial proximity can be visualized in Fig. 2c.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper demonstrates use case of identifying enriched cell-type pairs in spatial neighborhoods.",
