      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "To enable efficient processing of very large images, this pipeline utilizes lazy loading, image tiling and multiprocessing... The ImageContainer object stores multiple image layers with spatial dimensions x, y, z... Using image features, pixel-level information is related to the molecular profile in Anndata",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes lazy loading of images and efficient processing of large images, but does not explicitly discuss keeping 'computation graphs' or feature extraction results as lazy arrays. The emphasis is on lazy image I/O and tiling, not on deferred feature computation graphs.",
