      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Assemble adjacency and distance matrices into Compressed Sparse Row (CSR) format from flattened neighbor indices and distance arrays. This skill is essential for memory-efficient storage and fast linear algebra operations on large spatial graphs in bioinformatics workflows.",
