      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Using these representations, several analysis functions are defined to quantitatively describe tissue organization at the cellular (spatial neighborhood) and gene level (spatial statistics, spatially variable genes and ligand\u2013receptor interactions), to combine microscopy image information (image features and nuclei segmentation) with omics information and to interactively visualize high-resolution images.",
